  "title": "Procurement Officer",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Responsibilities</strong></p><ol><li>Prepare, compile and submit tender documents, and follow up on\n     tender submissions;</li><li>Assist in sourcing, reviewing and analysing tender\n     opportunities to ensure compliance with requirements;</li><li>Coordinate with internal departments (e.g. operations, finance,\n     technical teams) to obtain required information for tenders;</li><li>Support procurement activities including quotation requests,\n     price comparisons, contract documentation and record keeping;</li><li>Liaise with suppliers and provide administrative support\n     related to procurement matters;</li><li>Maintain proper records and documentation for tenders and\n     procurement in accordance with company procedures.</li></ol><p><strong>Job Requirements</strong></p><ol><li>Polytechnic Diploma or equivalent qualification;</li><li>Prior experience in tender, procurement or administrative\n     support roles is preferred;</li><li>Basic understanding of tender processes, contracts and\n     procurement procedures;</li><li>Detail-oriented with good organisational and documentation\n     skills;</li><li>Good communication skills to liaise with internal and external\n     stakeholders;</li><li>Proficient in Microsoft Office applications (Word, Excel,\n     PowerPoint).</li></ol>",
